      <title>华尔街捐助者为哈里斯的竞选提供快速致富的点子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/wall-street-donors-plan-get-rich-quick-ideas-for-harris-s-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街的民主党捐助者们在经历了几周漫无目的的担忧之后，终于有了明确的任务，他们担心总统乔·拜登会拖累民主党赢得白宫和国会多数席位的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/wall-street-donors-plan-get-rich-quick-ideas-for-harris-s-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临困难，舒尔茨仍坚持竞选连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/germany-s-scholz-sticks-to-reelection-bid-despite-fading-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 的执政联盟支持率正在逐渐下降，但他仍誓言将在明年的全国选举中寻求连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/germany-s-scholz-sticks-to-reelection-bid-despite-fading-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:59:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲁托任命反对党领袖姆巴迪为肯尼亚财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/kenyan-president-names-opposition-s-mbadi-as-treasury-secretary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托任命约翰·姆巴迪为财政部长，并扩大政府改革范围，以结束已造成至少 54 人死亡的反政府抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/kenyan-president-names-opposition-s-mbadi-as-treasury-secretary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯向西方国家装载第四艘受制裁的 Sovcomflot 油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/russia-loads-fourth-sanctioned-sovcomflot-tanker-in-snub-to-west</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯装载了国营 Sovcomflot PJSC 旗下的第四艘受制裁油轮，此举将考验七国集团的决心，因为七国集团正试图打击运送莫斯科石油的船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/russia-loads-fourth-sanctioned-sovcomflot-tanker-in-snub-to-west</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选“极难预测” 政策前景蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-sensationally-unpredictable-us-election-clouds-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国大选前不到四个月，民主党总统候选人的意外更换，给2025年及以后的经济政策前景带来了新的不确定因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-sensationally-unpredictable-us-election-clouds-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
